  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Better understanding of the immune responses to influenza vaccination is needed in order to
      understand situations of poor vaccine response. Adults will receive influenza vaccination and
      then have peripheral blood drawn at pre-defined intervals in order to study the lymphocyte
      responses.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
